<p>News analysis articles incorporate additional information, facts, and data that experts indicate provide useful and important context to the original event. A news analysis is based on factual reporting, adhering to the general guidelines for news reports. It generally follows a news report on the same subject.</p>

<p>The News Beat publishes four different types of articles: <a href="../article-types/?referrer=<?php echo urlencode(get_current_url());?>">news, analysis, opinion, and sponsored content</a>.</p>
